<plot>Policeman Dan Sampson (Brian Wimmer) happens to have the same badge # as deceased policeman Manny Torres, who died while on duty. The circumstances surrounding Torres' death, officially ruled a drug overdose, become Sampson's obsession. After Sampson begins investigating Torres' file and visiting Torres' widow, various parties begin making attempts on Sampson's life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?132779</url></doc>
